                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "13": {
                              "id": "13",
                              "speaker": "Astarion",
                              "text": "I know. Subtle, isn't it?",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {}
                            }
                          }
                        },
                        "6": {
                          "id": "6",
                          "speaker": "Player",
                          "text": "It might be safer to run. He wants you, after all.",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "8": {
                              "id": "8",
                              "speaker": "Astarion",
                              "text": "To where? For how long? If this worm shrivels, I'll be in his power from the second he lays eyes on me.",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "9": {
                                  "id": "9",
                                  "speaker": "Astarion",
                                  "text": "He has to die. While my body is still my own to command.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": true,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {}
                                }
                              }
                            }
                          }
                        },
                        "12": {
                          "id": "12",
                          "speaker": "Player",
                          "text": "We should ask around once in the city - maybe someone's heard something.",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "4": {
                              "id": "4",
                              "speaker": "Astarion",
                              "text": "I hope so, because I am not striking another deal with Raphael. Who knows what he'd demand this time.",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "15": {
                                  "id": "15",
                                  "speaker": "Astarion",
                                  "text": "But if the citizens of Baldur's Gate don't know anything, my brothers and sisters might. Cazador is a master of secrets, but the other spawn must have seen something.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": true,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {}
                                }
                              }
                            }
                          }
                        },
                        "3": {
                          "id": "3",
                          "speaker": "Player",
                          "text": "Raphael's playing a dangerous game, giving you Mephistopheles' secrets.",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "2": {
                              "id": "2",
                              "speaker": "Astarion",
                              "text": "Mephistopheles is one of the Lords of the Nine Hells. Raphael is not going to let any ire be tracked back to him.",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "14": {
                                  "id": "14",
                                  "speaker": "Astarion",
                                  "text": "Perhaps Raphael even will gain from setting us on this course. Who can say?",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "5": {
                                      "id": "5",
                                      "speaker": "Astarion",
                                      "text": "All I know is I need to unravel the secrets around Cazador's ritual. And I can only do that in Baldur's Gate.",
                                      "context": "",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
